page_description: Learn more about how the Azure OpenAI embeddings API uses cosine similarity for document search and to measure similarity between texts.
chunk_content: Next steps* Learn more about using Azure OpenAI and embeddings to perform document search with our embeddings tutorial.* Store your embeddings and perform vector (similarity) search using Azure Cosmos DB for MongoDB vCore, Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL ,  Azure SQL Database or Azure Database for PostgreSQL - Flexible Server.
